overview: Teejay (Teejay Marquez), a new student from the Philippines, made hysterical girls at school. Teejay is famous for Dubsmash videos that are often uploaded on social media! Teejay lives with his happy family who just moved to Indonesia. Elsa (Jessica Mila) who has a broken home family background, feels comfortable when close to Teejay. Elsa has never found anyone who can understand her, including Marvel (Verrel Bramasta), her boyfriend. This relationship makes Marvel jealous.
title: Dubsmash
